{
  "name": "w02_z02.ks",
  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "line": "「おはよう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000333\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "line": "「おはよう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "line": "ホームルーム前ギリギリの時間に教室へと到着する。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000079\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "line": "「おっす、二人とも」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000080\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "line": "「……ん？　なんかお前たち、疲れた顔してないか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "line": "ずいっと十兵衛が顔をのぞき込んでくる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "line": "「そうか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000334\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "line": "「実際、和哉は疲れてるんでしょう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000335\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "line": "「……昨晩、あんなことがあったし」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "line": "「うぐっ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "line": "今朝はドタバタしていて気付かなかったが、どうやら\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "line": "智花は昨晩のアレをまだ気にしているらしい。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000081\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "line": "「ほほ〜う……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "line": "「な……なんだよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000082\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "line": "「いや、みなまで言うな和哉。分かってる。俺には\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "line": "　分かりすぎるほど分かっているぞ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 107,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "line": "うすら寒くなる程、熱意を込めて頷く十兵衛が、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "line": "いきなり肩に腕を回してくる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 114,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 115,
      "line": "「な、なんだよ？　なにを分かってるっていうんだ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 120,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000083\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 121,
      "line": "「長男争奪戦の幕開けなんだろ？　な？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129,
      "line": "「なっ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 137,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000084\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 138,
      "line": "「おい図星か！？　図星なのかよ和哉！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 142,
      "line": "「うぐっ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 147,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 148,
      "line": "どうやらカマをかけただけだったらしい……不覚にも\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 149,
      "line": "まんまと引っかかってしまった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 154,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000336\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155,
      "line": "「ちょっと、なんの話をしてるのよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 161,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000085\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 162,
      "line": "「男同士の大事な話だっ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 167,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 168,
      "line": "取り残された智花が、ますます不機嫌そうに頬を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 169,
      "line": "ふくらませている。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 175,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000086\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 176,
      "line": "「智花が怒ってるってことは、智花じゃない他の誰かと\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 177,
      "line": "　なんかあったんだろ？　教えてくれよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 187,
      "line": "……………………\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 190,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 191,
      "line": "言えるわけがない。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 194,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 195,
      "line": "十兵衛好みの話ではあっても、あまりに非日常的すぎる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 205,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000087\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 206,
      "line": "「なんだよなんだよ〜、智花が怒るようなことで、お前が\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 207,
      "line": "　赤くなっちゃうようなことなのか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 211,
      "line": "「う、うるさいな。十兵衛はなんでそんなにテンションが\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 212,
      "line": "　高いんだよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 218,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000088\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 219,
      "line": "「そりゃー、お前は俺にとって姉妹萌え最後の\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 220,
      "line": "　希望だからな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 223,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 224,
      "line": "「なんだよそれ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000089\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 230,
      "line": "「で？　今のところは誰がいいんだよ、お兄ちゃん？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 235,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 236,
      "line": "「気色悪い言い方するなよ。それに……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 241,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000090\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 242,
      "line": "「それに？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 245,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246,
      "line": "「誰か一人を選ぶことには、やっぱり抵抗があるよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 257,
      "line": "@Talk name=いずみ voice=IS000337\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 258,
      "line": "「『誰がかずちゃんと一緒に暮らせるのか』……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000337\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264,
      "line": "「！！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 269,
      "line": "@Talk name=いずみ voice=IS000338\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 270,
      "line": "「それは、誰がかずちゃんの心を射止めるのか、という\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 271,
      "line": "　ことと同義だわ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 276,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000338\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 277,
      "line": "「は……話が飛躍しすぎよ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 282,
      "line": "@Talk name=いずみ voice=IS000339\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 283,
      "line": "「そうかしら？　お父さんたちの離婚話がどうなるかは\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 284,
      "line": "　分からないけれど……永遠に姉弟みんな一緒という\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 285,
      "line": "　わけにはいかないでしょう？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 290,
      "line": "@Talk name=いずみ voice=IS000340\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 291,
      "line": "「そうなったとき、かずちゃんが一緒に居たいと思う\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 292,
      "line": "　相手が誰なのか……はっきりさせておくべきじゃ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 293,
      "line": "　ないかしら？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 303,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 304,
      "line": "いずみ姉さんのあの言葉を思い出すたびに、考えずには\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 305,
      "line": "いられない。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 308,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 309,
      "line": "俺の選択が、姉妹たちの人生を変えてしまうんじゃ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 310,
      "line": "ないかって——\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 315,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000091\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 316,
      "line": "「……そんな深刻そうな顔するなよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 321,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000092\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 322,
      "line": "「お前がお前なりに考えて出した答えなら、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 323,
      "line": "　どんな答えでも納得してくれるだろ、倉野姉妹は」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 326,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 327,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 332,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000093\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 333,
      "line": "「なんたってお前は溺愛されてるもんなあ！　そうだろ、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 334,
      "line": "　智花」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 340,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000339\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 341,
      "line": "「なぁっ！？　だ、誰が誰を溺愛してるって言うのよっ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 344,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 345,
      "line": "いきなり話を振られたせいか、智花がビクッと反応する。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 351,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000094\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 352,
      "line": "「そんなの言うまでもないだろ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 358,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000340\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 359,
      "line": "「な、なによその目は……十兵衛のくせにじろじろ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 360,
      "line": "　見ないで」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 366,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000095\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 367,
      "line": "「俺たち幼馴染みだよな！？　なんで通りすがりの変態を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 368,
      "line": "　見るような扱いなんだよ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 374,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000341\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 375,
      "line": "「当たり前でしょう。和哉に変なことばかり\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 376,
      "line": "　吹き込むんだから、迷惑きわまりない変態だわ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 382,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000096\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 383,
      "line": "「変なことじゃないぞ！　人生を正しい方向へ導くための\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 384,
      "line": "　バイブルを指南してるんだ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 387,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 388,
      "line": "「真顔で力説するなよ、そんなこと……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 394,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000342\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 395,
      "line": "「呆れた変態ね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 401,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000097\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 402,
      "line": "「フッフッフ、バカにしていられるのも今のうちだぞ智花」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 407,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000343\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 408,
      "line": "「だからなによ、十兵衛のくせにその余裕は」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 419,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000098\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 420,
      "line": "「男のバイブル、それすなわち——男へのアプローチ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 421,
      "line": "　秘伝の書と言っても過言ではないっっっ！！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 427,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000344\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 428,
      "line": "「はあ？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 431,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 432,
      "line": "おお、十兵衛が智花を懐柔しようとしている。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 435,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 436,
      "line": "まあ、こんな説明で智花がほだされるとは思えないが……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 445,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000345\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 446,
      "line": "「男の子が女の子にちやほやされるものなんでしょ？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 447,
      "line": "　どうしてそれが……アプローチの参考になるのよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 452,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000099\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 453,
      "line": "「男を魅了するためには、可愛さが必要だろ。ちやほや\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 454,
      "line": "　されている主人公を落とすためには、それだけ突出した\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 455,
      "line": "　可愛さが必要になってくる」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 460,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000346\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 461,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 466,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000100\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 467,
      "line": "「男の憧れと郷愁と妄想を凝縮して抽出した\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 468,
      "line": "　ヒロインたちに魅了されない男はいない！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 475,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000347\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 476,
      "line": "「！！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 481,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000101\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 482,
      "line": "「つまり！　これを読み解き、体得すれば……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 487,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000102\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 488,
      "line": "「どんな鈍感男でも、振り向かせることが可能になる！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 495,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000103\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 496,
      "line": "「……かもしれない」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 501,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 502,
      "line": "やっと十兵衛の熱弁が終わった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 505,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 506,
      "line": "智花もさぞ呆れていることだろう。なにせ、珍しく饒舌に\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 507,
      "line": "なったかと思えば、内容が不純すぎる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 513,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000348\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 514,
      "line": "「い、一理ある……のかしら？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 519,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 520,
      "line": "「ええ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 523,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 524,
      "line": "気がつけば、智花が神妙な顔で頷いていた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 530,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000349\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 531,
      "line": "「どんな鈍感男も……体得すれば……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 532,
      "line": "　アプローチ秘伝の書……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 535,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 536,
      "line": "「智花、智花？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 539,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 540,
      "line": "だめだ、なにかにとりつかれたように十兵衛の言葉を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 541,
      "line": "反芻している。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 548,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000104\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 549,
      "line": "「フハハハハ、思い知ったか智花！　極意の指南が\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 550,
      "line": "　欲しければ、和哉と一緒に教えてやらなくもないぞ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 556,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000350\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 557,
      "line": "「お、おねが——」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 564,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000351\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 565,
      "line": "「——って、なんで十兵衛にそんなこと頼まなくちゃいけ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 566,
      "line": "　ないのよ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 577,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000105\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 578,
      "line": "「ぶはぁっ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 584,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 585,
      "line": "智花の投げたかばんが、十兵衛の顔にクリティカルヒット\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 586,
      "line": "した。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 592,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000352\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 593,
      "line": "「だ、だいたいそれが本当なら、十兵衛は今頃彼女くらい\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 594,
      "line": "　できてるはずでしょ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 603,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000106\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 604,
      "line": "「ぐはっ！？　おま、物理攻撃よりよっぽど傷ついたぞ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 607,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 608,
      "line": "十兵衛の言っていることが正しければ、男が女の子に\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 609,
      "line": "モテたいなら、少女漫画を読めばいいってことになる\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 610,
      "line": "からな。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 613,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 614,
      "line": "彼女居ない歴＝年齢のおかげでバレる嘘ほど、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 615,
      "line": "もの悲しいものはないな……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 621,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000353\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 622,
      "line": "「まったく……危うくだまされるところだったわ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 625,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 626,
      "line": "ふうっ、と額の汗を拭う智花。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 629,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 630,
      "line": "「意外だな、智花があそこまで信じかけるなんて」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 636,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000354\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 637,
      "line": "「な、なんですってぇ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 640,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 641,
      "line": "なぜか、怒りの矛先がこちらに向いた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 644,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 645,
      "line": "俺はなにかおかしなことを言ったのだろうか？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 650,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000355\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 651,
      "line": "「………………鈍感っ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 657,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 658,
      "line": "言い捨てて、放り投げたかばんを拾って、自分の席へと\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 659,
      "line": "座ってしまう。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 665,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 666,
      "line": "「どうしたんだろう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 672,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000107\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 673,
      "line": "「……それでこそ我らが希望だ、和哉」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 676,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 677,
      "line": "「十兵衛、まだ生きてたのか」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 683,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000108\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 684,
      "line": "「お前ら姉弟、俺に冷たすぎないか！？　泣くぞ！？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 685,
      "line": "　娘が居候と混浴してるのに助けに行けない父親くらい\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 686,
      "line": "　泣くぞ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 689,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 690,
      "line": "「はいはい、悪かったって」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 693,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 694,
      "line": "例えはよく分からないが泣かれるとうっとうしいので、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 695,
      "line": "とりあえず助け起こしてやることにする。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 701,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000109\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 702,
      "line": "「ふうー、まったく……智花はつくづく苦労人だな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 708,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 709,
      "line": "服についたほこりを払いながら、十兵衛が独りごちる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 714,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 715,
      "line": "十兵衛の言葉に、智花の方へ視線を送ると——\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 722,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000356\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 723,
      "line": "「あっ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 728,
      "line": "@Talk name=智花 voice=TM000357\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 729,
      "line": "「……フンッ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 735,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 736,
      "line": "思い切り目を逸らされてしまった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 743,
      "line": "@Talk name=静子 voice=SZ000021\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 744,
      "line": "「みなさ〜ん、おはようございます〜」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 750,
      "line": "@Talk name=静子 voice=SZ000022\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 751,
      "line": "「うふふ、今日はチャイムより早く来てみました〜」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 754,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 755,
      "line": "今日も相変わらずふわふわしている岡野先生が、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 756,
      "line": "教室へ入ってきた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 761,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 762,
      "line": "クラスメイトたちが口々に褒めながら、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 763,
      "line": "あめやチョコレートをカンパしている。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 771,
      "line": "@Talk name=無音/静子\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 772,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 775,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 776,
      "line": "岡野先生と目が合った。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 783,
      "line": "@Talk name=静子 voice=SZ000023\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 784,
      "line": "「うふふ〜」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 791,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛 voice=JB000110\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 792,
      "line": "「ほら和哉、お前からのおやつをご所望らしいぞ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 795,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 796,
      "line": "「ああ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 801,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 802,
      "line": "十兵衛に促されて、俺も先生へチョコレートを一粒\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 803,
      "line": "さしだした。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 809,
      "line": "@Talk name=静子 voice=SZ000024\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 810,
      "line": "「ありがとうございます、倉野くん〜。先生、褒められて\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 811,
      "line": "　伸びる子なんですよ〜」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 814,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 815,
      "line": "「そうですか。今以上に伸びたら、学食の責任者に\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 816,
      "line": "　なれたりするかもしれませんね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 822,
      "line": "@Talk name=静子 voice=SZ000025\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 823,
      "line": "「わあ〜、それはとってもすてきです〜。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 824,
      "line": "　先生がんばりますね〜〜」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 831,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 832,
      "line": "ググッとガッツポーズをする岡野先生に笑みを返して、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 833,
      "line": "自分の席へと戻る。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 841,
      "line": "@Talk name=十兵衛/心の声 voice=JB000111\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 842,
      "line": "『お前がお前なりに考えて出した答えなら、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 843,
      "line": "　どんな答えでも納得してくれるだろ、倉野姉妹は』\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 846,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 847,
      "line": "“俺の決めたことになら、姉妹が納得してくれる”\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 850,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 851,
      "line": "確かに、十兵衛の言うことも一理ある……なぜなら姉妹\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 852,
      "line": "たちは、俺の判断を全面的に信頼してくれているからだ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 856,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 857,
      "line": "しかし、だからこそ、俺の責任は重い。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 860,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 861,
      "line": "どんな答えを出せば、みんなが幸せになれるのか……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 864,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 865,
      "line": "長男として、俺はそれを真剣に考えなくてはいけないのだ。\r\n"
    }
  ]
}